# Meinhold-576: Sabidussi coset graph of G₂(2)

The **Meinhold-576** graph (576 vertices, 7-regular, girth 6) is the coset graph
`Sab(G₂(2), C₇:C₃)` with `576 = 12096/21` vertices.

Named after Nick Meinhold, co-founder of Imagineering Melbourne.

